  <h2>
    <span class="">以下豆列推荐</span>
      &nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;
      <span class="pl">&nbsp;(
          <a href="https://book.douban.com/subject/1044515/doulists">全部</a>
        ) </span>

  </h2>


    <div id="db-doulist-section" class="indent">
      <ul class="bs">
          <li class=""><a class="" href="https://www.douban.com/doulist/15641/" target="_blank">王怡的读书单：自由主义</a>
                <span class="pl">(海若)</span>
            </li>
          <li class=""><a class="" href="https://www.douban.com/doulist/206445/" target="_blank">中央戏剧学院戏剧文学系阅读书目（戏剧）。</a>
